data.description: Welcome to your waterfront haven! Revel in the tranquility of nature right from your backyard with gorgeous water views. This well-maintained 3-bedroom, 2 bath home puts on display how it's been lovingly cared for at every turn. This home offers a fantastic bonus room - perfect for use as an office, guest room where you can use the built in murphy bed, an exercise room, craft room, endless options on how you could use this flex space. You'll love the large primary bedroom suite which features a spacious walk-in closet, located on its own side of the home for a true split plan, allowing for privacy when hosting guests. In addition to the breakfast nook/dining area, there is additional seating at the countertop, making this just one more reason it's perfect for family gatherings or entertaining friends. Beautiful and functional, light & bright kitchen with granite countertops and tons of cabinet space. The oversized 2-car garage provides ample space, park your boat or other toys or 2 vehicles plus storage. This property includes recent updates on some of the major systems such as a new hot water heater installed in 2023, a brand-new roof in 2022, a brand new screened-in lanai in 2020 and a new HVAC in 2017. The interior received a modern update in 2017. Plus, benefit from a transferrable Termite Bond for added peace of mind and prepare to enjoy this low maintenance turn-key home. Located on the freshwater canal, step into outdoor bliss with an above-ground pool that conveys with the property and room for a Jacuzzi. Indulge in picturesque sunsets on your private waterfront dock where you can fish for bass, bowfins, brim & more. Additional entertainment space awaits just outside the screened-in rear lanai, featuring a fire-pit and garden boxes - a perfect spot to appreciate the Florida lifestyle. Palm Coast sits on 70 miles of canals, the Intracoastal Waterway, and stunning Flagler Beach just 10-mile ride away. Palm Coast boasts parks, trails, fishing, boating, and premier tennis and golf facilities. All your conveniences are within reach such as grocery shopping, dining, parks, I-95, and more in close proximity. Enjoy easy access to St. Augustine and Daytona Beach, each just a scenic 30-minute drive away. This home will be where YOUR heart is! Take a private tour today!
